						               													<description>The Scafford Gang are one of the most dangerous bands of outlaws in the West! Ruthless Mutants lead by Colonel Scafford and his trusty Lieutenants, the Scafford Gang robs trains and towns across the countryside, making their hideouts in the caves and abandoned mines up in the hills. Former Confederates in the Civil War, they despise the law and use their hideous mutations to fill their pockets with gold and Dark Stone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This set adds new large Enemy Record Sheets for 2 of the dangerous Scafford Lieutenants &amp;ndash;Captain Burns and 'Ol&amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#153; One Eye' Jackson, making them full Enemy mini-bosses. It also includes new outlaw-themed Gear and Artifact cards, as well as a set of new Threat cards that combine various Scafford themed Enemies together, and even Epic Threats to face off against a more dangerous version of each of these Lieutenants with their gang.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game supplement enhances the Scafford Gang Deluxe Enemy Pack and Dark Stone Brutes Enemy Pack, as well as the Resin Enemy Figures for Captain Burns and 'Ol&amp;rsquo; One Eye' Jackson. Those Enemy Packs and resin Miniatures are NOT INCLUDED.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;CONTENTS&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Captain Burns Enemy Sheet&amp;#10;     Ol 'One Eye' Jackson Enemy Sheet&amp;#10;     Card #468 Captain Burns and D3+1 Scafford Gang (Low Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #469 Captain Burns, P Scafford Gang, and 1 Dark Stone Brute (Medium Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #470 Captain Burns, PP Scafford Gang, and 1 Dark Stone Brute (High Threat; includes Heavy Brute trait)&amp;#10;     Card #471 Captain Burns, PP Scafford Gang, and 1 Dark Stone Brute (Epic Threat; includes Leader and Super Brute traits)&amp;#10;     Card #472 Ol 'One Eye&amp;quot; Jackson, 2 Scafford Gang, and 1 Dark Stone Brute (Low Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #473 Ol 'One Eye&amp;quot; Jackson, D3+1 Scafford Gang, and 2 Dark Stone Brutes (Medium Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #474 Ol 'One Eye&amp;quot; Jackson, D6+1 Scafford Gang, and 3 Dark Stone Brutes (High Threat)&amp;#10;     Card #475 Ol 'One Eye&amp;quot; Jackson, P+1 Scafford Gang, and 3 Dark Stone Brutes (Epic Threat; includes Leader trait)&amp;#10;     Card #476 Mutant's Satchel (Gear)&amp;#10;     Card #477 Scafford Sabre (Mine Artifact)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
